.ti -.5i
ccoptions: \-O
.br
Options given directly to \fIcc\fR\0(1).
The most common is \*(lq\-M\*(rq if you're running \fIMH\fR on an ALTOS.
This defaults to \*(lq\-O\*(rq.  If you define this and want to 
