Support for the UCI BBoards facility.
d225 6
a264 14

.ti -.5i
popbboards: off
.br
Support for the UCI BBoards facility via the POP service.
Requires both bboards and pop to be enabled.

.ti -.5i
nntpbboards: off
.br
Support for the UCI BBoards facility to read the Network News
via the NNTP.
Requires bboards to be enabled.  You cannot enable both
popbboards and nntpbboards.
